snippet.title: Haven & Hearth -- World 16 Trailer
snippet.description:
World 16 Announcement Trailer. World 16 begins on Friday 1st of November, 2024.

World 16 will also be made available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3051280/Haven__Hearth/
